summary:
Some potential shiny Wooloo designs and a sheared to full wool for each. 
The black shiny is most likely. The whole “black...
body:
Some potential shiny Wooloo designs and a sheared to full wool for each.

The black shiny is most likely. The whole “black sheep” thing ya know?

The golden boi was inspired by brown sheep, but also Golden Fleece. I just really liked the idea of a golden sheep

The last one is based off a real sheep breed called the Scottish Blackface. No way in hell they give us spotty cloud, but it’s pretty damn cute.

I’m guessing if we get a sheared Wooloo it will be in a mini game. It’s also possible that a payer would be able to sheer their own Wooloo and sell the fibers, but it’s not likely
